summary: Leader encompasses profiles such as Jan Hein Hoogstad, alias Yeehaa, a self-taught software architect and entrepreneur. Jan strengthens team performance through technology, founded Varias to assist startups, and organizes the Superconnectors event, linking startups with key individuals in the Dutch tech ecosystem.
excerpt: Jan Hein Hoogstad, also known as Yeehaa, is an entrepreneur who creates solutions to improve team performance, founded Varias, and organizes Superconnectors to connect startups and influencers.
